## Skill & Agent Usage in Claude / Claude Code CLI

### 1. `/proofread` вЂ” Proofreading Documents

```bash
# Single file
/proofread and /proofreader, use the skill and agent to proofread "papers/***.docx"

# Batch process all files
/proofread all

### 2. `/review-paper` вЂ” Manuscript / Paper Review
# Review a specific manuscript
/review-paper, use the skill to reviw papers/my_paper.docx

# Review LaTeX or PDF
/review-paper papers/research_note.tex

### 3. ` /lit-review ` вЂ” Literature Search and Synthesis
# Review a research topic
/lit-review, use the skill to review the topic "climate risk and corporate finance"

# Use a specific paper title or research question
/lit-review, use the skill to review the papers/ "Fama-French 3-factor model"

